chat.msg: hi there! que comience el juego!!
hello
hey, buddy! i'm currently at the start point, and i see a twig to my left leading to a small island with a tiger
how should we move?
head to the tiger
alright, made it to the tiger island
now, there's a butterfly island to my southeast and another big island with a parrot on the southwest. which one is our next move?
go to the parrot
awesome! i'm now on the big island with the parrot happily chirping away
also i spot an elephant to my left and three rocks leading to a frog island on the southeast. what's next, buddy?
use the rocks to get to the frog
hopped over the rocks, and now at the frog island
i see a crocodile to my left and the elephant's big island to the left of the croc. next step?
follow the crocodile to the elephant
been there, done that! back at the elephant's island
now head over to the giraffe
roger that! i'm chillin' with the giraffe now
head to the snake
slithered my way to the snake! now, we've got the treasure, 2 steps to the east
what do you say, should we go for it?
yes, go to the treasure
voila! we've got the booty
all that glitters is ours now! *finished*
hola, you ready?
yes
great! first, take a few steps west, towards that wooden bench and the trail
don't walk too far, we're not going to the florist stand
i'm at the bench
good job! now, let's play a bit
turn around, 180 degrees to your left. we're crossing that trail again, heading back towards our furry friend
back at the dog
super! now head straight down, southwards, sticking to the trail
you'll pass another white dog who's chilling next to a checkered picnic. let's move!
i'm at the other dog
cool! let's keep going
hop over the mat, give those berries a little touch, and move on the path towards the west
do you mean by the deer?
nah, we're not there yet
instead, look for a wooden branch to cross the river to the north. you'll see it!
i crossed the river on the branch to the north
spot on! you're doing great!
what next
now, let's dance around this green bush, circle it from the right side, but don't touch it! got it?
i circled around the bush
perfect! head towards the florist stand that's nearby, but then we're turning west
ready? let's go!
yes
well done! you'll see a big bridge coming up, let's pass it on the west side
i am across the bridge
you're a natural! now, go south a bit, you'll spot two elderly folks on a bench
don't disturb them!
i am south of the elderly folks
look around, see the wooden branch and a green bush? excellent, you're in the right spot! keep up the good work!
yes
let's continue east, between the branch and the bush, only a few steps away!
hey, estas listo?
yes
cool! i'm at the north end of the map in a tent
where to next, buddy?
go south past the dog
right on, i see that good boy on my left and a fire on my right
all set to go further south?
head towards the fire
ok, passing by the fire now
i see a cool red mushroom nearby. how about next, pal?
head south of the mushroom onto the road but before the car
alright, i'm on the road now, just before the blue car
where to now, mate?
head west to the fork in the road, then go south past the telescope
roger that, i've passed the blue telescope
head west on the road until you reach the cabin, then head northwest until you reach it
gotcha! made it to the house, surrounded by some big rocks
*finished*
hola, q tal? ready to play?
ready
perfect! look for three palm trees
got it? now, head towards the first one in the southwest
i am at the palm tree
cool! now turn right, scoot past the second palm and swerve left before you reach the third one
go south
how far south
just a few steps till you meet a brown puppy
stay to his left, veer a little left, then swing right back to south
between the rocks?
yeah, exactly! make your way between the big rock (west) and the small one (east) and hit the water
i see a crab
duke it out, my friend! now take a right, keeping the big rock close and follow the shoreline west
now i see a shark
whoa! sharp turn to your right
stay safe!
volleyball
cool find! keep it on your right, head towards land between the medium rock and the ball
continue north
i see a speaker and a tent
super! wedge yourself between them
the tent on your left, speaker on your right, and keep moving to the northwest
i am northwest of the tent
nice job! now curve around the tent in an arc
don't go too far, we're not heading for the sea
now there is a kayak
awesome! head west, under the kayak
